Interface GenericResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GroupableResource, Indexable, Refreshable<GenericResource>, Resource, Updatable<GenericResource.UpdateWithApiVersion>, Wrapper<GenericResourceInner>

    public interface GenericResource
extends GroupableResource, Refreshable<GenericResource>, Updatable<GenericResource.UpdateWithApiVersion>, Wrapper<GenericResourceInner>
    An immutable client-side representation of an Azure generic resource.
